workflow:
  name: Publication media

before_script:
  - echo "bob" > username.txt
  - echo "username:"
  - cat username.txt
  - echo "password:"
  - echo "*****"
  - echo "you are logged in to your account"

after_script:
  - rm username.txt
  - echo "you are logged out!"

share_post:
  script:
    - echo "account owner:"
    - cat username.txt
    - echo "sharing post..."
    - sleep 10s
    - echo "post shared successfully!"

delete_post:
  script:
    - echo "account owner:"
    - cat username.txt
    - echo "sharing post..."
    - sleep 10s
    - echo "post shared successfully!"


Noted : before script and after script can be defined at job level or at pipline level where it is common for all the jobs defined in teh file as mentioned above
